Heal_Other.help: Heals a single targeted ally. You cannot use this power to heal yourself. Recharge: Fast

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} heals you for {Damage} points of damage.

Healing_Aura.help: Healing Aura restores some Hit Points to you and all nearby heroes. Healing Aura is not as potent as Heal Other, but can heal multiple targets at once. Recharge: Moderate
Healing_Aura.targetHelp: Healing Aura restores some Hit Points to you and all nearby heroes. Healing Aura is not as potent as Heal Other, but can heal multiple targets at once. Recharge: Moderate

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} heals you for {Damage} points of damage.

Fortitude.help: Heroes can greatly increase an ally's powers as well as increase their perception and resistances.
Fortitude.shortHelp: Ally +DEF, +DMG, +ACC, +Res(Disorient, Hold, Sleep, Immobilize, Fear, Confuse), +Perception
Fortitude.targetHelp: Heroes can greatly increase an ally's powers as well as increase their perception and resistances.
Fortitude.targetShortHelp: Ally +DEF, +DMG, +ACC, +Res(Disorient, Hold, Sleep, Immobilize, Fear, Confuse), +Perception

Regeneration_Aura.help: The Regeneration Aura dramatically increases the healing rate of all nearby heroes for a limited time. Emitting this Aura costs you a lot of Endurance, and it takes a long time to recharge. Recharge: Very Long
Regeneration_Aura.targetHelp: The Regeneration Aura is improving your Healing Rate, allowing you to battle longer!
Regeneration_Aura.attackerHit: You increase the Hit Point Regeneration of {PlayerDest}.

Levitate.help: You can send a single target violently into the air, then slam him to the ground for Smashing damage. This power can bring flying foes to the ground. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Moderate
Levitate.targetHelp: You can send a single target violently into the air, then slam him to the ground for Smashing damage. This power can bring flying foes to the ground. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Moderate

messages.attackerHit: You knock {PlayerDest} off their feet with your {PowerName}!
messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} knocks you off your feet with their {PowerName}!

messages.attackerHit: You hit {PlayerDest} with your {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Smashing damage.
messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} hits you with their {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Smashing damage.

Dominate.help: Psychic energy tears at your mind rendering you helpless, lost in your own mind and unable to defend yourself.
Dominate.targetHelp: Psychic energy tears at your mind rendering you helpless, lost in your own mind and unable to defend yourself.

Terrify.help: This power Terrifies foes within a cone area in front of you, causing them to tremble in Fear uncontrollably. The affect is so frightening and overwhelming, that the target takes real damage from the physiological response to this Psionic attack. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Slow

messages.attackerHit: You hit {PlayerDest} with your {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Psionic damage.
messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} hits you with their {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Psionic damage.

Mass_Hypnosis.help: The Hero has hypnotized you. You are helpless for a while, unless something snaps you out of it.
Mass_Hypnosis.targetHelp: The Hero has hypnotized you. You are helpless for a while, unless something snaps you out of it.
